quran[14{c,v,t}:
106,1,chunkay Quresh manoos hue
106,2,( yani ) jaray aur garmi ke safron se manoos
106,3,lehaza unn ko chahiye ke iss ghar ke Rab ki ibadat karen
106,4,jis ne unhen bhook se bacha kar khanay ko diya aur khauf se bacha kar aman ataa kya
107,1,tum ne dekha uss shakhs ko jo akhirat ki jaza o saza ko jhutlata hai ?
107,2,wohi to hai jo yateem ko dhakkay deta hai
107,3,aur maskeen ko khana dainay par nahi aksata
107,4,phir tabahi hai unn namaz parhnay walon ke liye
107,5,jo apni namaz se ghaflat brtte hain
107,6,jo riya kaari karte hain
107,7,aur mamooli zaroorat ki cheeze ( logon ko ) dainay se guraiz karte hain
108,1,( ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ) hum ne tumhe kousar ataa kar diya
108,2,pas tum apne Rab hi ke liye namaz parho aur qurbani karo
108,3,tumhara dushman hi jarr kata hai
